_sText:
What you get here, is a small map, which is created with a great amount of attention to graphical detail. This attention is, in part, expressed by very detailed brushwork, soundscapes, a 3D-skybox and, new in this release, HDR.
The maps setting is, as the name suggests, some industrial estate which is laid out for a maximum of 20 players, while still creating an intense gaming experience for smaller amounts of players.
